HEADWORD: Pulpy
<hw>Pulp"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Like pulp; consisting
of pulp; soft; fleshy; succulent; <as>as, the <er>pulpy</er> covering of
a nut; the <ex>pulpy</ex> substance of a peach or a
cherry.</as></def>⟦br⟧
